        "name": "Annual Recurring Revenue (ARR)",
        "definition": "Annualized recurring subscription revenue; ARR_t = sum of monthly subscription value * 12 across all active subscribers at time t.",
        "source_system": "stripe",
        "cadence": "daily",
        "rationale": "Per Tunguz / Reichheld: ARR is the canonical SaaS revenue metric. As a north-star it has the virtue of being source-system definite and the limitation of lagging behavior.",
